- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with control of dynamical systems, which falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): The paper uses linear temporal logic (LTL) specifications and formal methods, which are relevant to this sub-category. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper discusses the computation of control strategies, which involves programming concepts and techniques. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses adaptive control methods, which are a subfield of AI. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper includes case studies that involve control of robotic systems, which is relevant to this sub-category.
